text: Nanda Kishor Pun (born 23 October 1966) is a Nepalese politician. He was the vice president of Nepal (Nepali: नेपालका उपराष्ट्रपतिहरू, Nēpālakā uparāṣṭrapatiharū), the deputy to the head of state of Nepal. == References == Category:Living people Category:1966 births Category:Vice presidents Category:Nepalese politicians
title: Nanda Kishor Pun
